room_title: Escape room "The Egyptian Tomb" by Escape Room Mystery in King of Prussia
room_address: 840 1st Avenue, Suite 500 King of Prussia, PA 19406
room_description: Archaeology has never been more challenging and possibly deadly! Find yourselves locked in an ancient Egyptian tomb with puzzles and surprises that can lead to your freedom. But hurry, time is short, you may be locked in forever, or worse! Can you figure out the hidden clues, avoid cunning traps, uncover hidden passageways and escape the tomb?
